Open Business: 

"described by its creators as a “punk fantasy adventure�?, is innovative in a few ways. It’s an independent, feature-length animated series, for starters, made on a budget of less than $10,000 (where conventional animated feature films would cost more like $100,000,000). It’s made using Machinima technology, and shot using an invisible badger as a cameraman. And, despite the fact it’s being produced by a professional production company, Strange Company, it’s being released under a Creative Commons license, free for the download."
